  "title": "Warehouse Assistant Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title:</strong> Warehouse Supervisor (Gul Circle | from $2,300 onwards | 5.5 Days)</p><p><strong>About the Role: </strong>We are looking for a reliable and hands-on Warehouse Supervisor to lead our team at Gul Circle. If you are an experienced leader who can plan logistics schedules but is also willing to step in and drive a forklift when needed, we want to hear from you.</p><p><strong>Work Information:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Salary:</strong> $2,300 (Negotiable based on experience) + Overtime pay </p></li><li><p><strong>Location:</strong> 1 Gul Circle (Sheltered ramp-up warehouse with wall fans; Air-con office)</p></li><li><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5.5 Days</p><ul><li><p>Mon to Fri: 830 am to 530pm</p></li><li><p>Sat: 830am to 1230pm</p></li></ul></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Team Leadership:</strong> Manage and deploy a team of 4-6 warehouse assistants.</p></li><li><p><strong>Logistics Planning:</strong> Coordinate container stuffing/unstuffing and manage trucking in/out schedules.</p></li><li><p><strong>Operations:</strong> Ensure all jobs are followed up on and SOPs/Safety procedures are strictly followed.</p></li><li><p><strong>Documentation:</strong> Ensure correct filing of documents.</p></li><li><p><strong>Backup Support:</strong> Be ready to assist with data entry (SAP/Excel) or operate Forklift/Reach Truck during staff shortages.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Must be Singaporean or PR.</strong></p></li><li><p>Possess a valid Forklift License.</p></li><li><p>Computer literate (Familiar with Email, Excel, and SAP).</p></li></ul>",
